s/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算係人地都劈咗炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ffe50154bd44b712e1fe69492553e19fd82c16","tid":156769,"uid":72369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱1823咗<br />\n佢話口頭同書面都可以係合約條款<br />\n叫我地睇下間公司既員工守則<br />\n同問下其他員工有咪有類似經歷<br />\n最後suggest我地去搵勞資關係科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點搵類似經歷既員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算係人地都劈咗炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係你就果少少錢算9數<br />\n直接爆佢公司名出來"},{"pid":"06f5bd10c148a6cae4086701d0b5ae0f2e61c56a","tid":156769,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:45:41.000Z","msg":"依家D人真幸福<br />\n我第一份工已經俾人剋扣通知金，仲打乜鬼1823<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻乜撚都唔簽，拎埋張打咭紀錄上勞工處備案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1450da73c6dca776977b2baff0404097f24cd0c","tid":156769,"uid":54610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱1823咗<br />\n佢話口頭同書面都可以係合約條款<br />\n叫我地睇下間公司既員工守則<br />\n同問下其他員工有咪有類似經歷<br />\n最後suggest我地去搵勞資關係科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點搵類似經歷既員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算係人地都劈咗炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係你就果少少錢算9數<br />\n直接爆佢公司名出來</blockquote><br />\n果幾舊水無所謂，係為啖氣<br />\n整d 仆街arrangement搞到我朋友辭工<br />\n辭完工仲要比唔足數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e25e31004c82f76549f87bb60848e10ebbead59","tid":156769,"uid":54610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家D人真幸福<br />\n我第一份工已經俾人剋扣通知金，仲打乜鬼1823<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class